title: Hour 1 - The New Normal for Tom Brady and the Buccaneers
itunes:title: Hour 1 - The New Normal for Tom Brady and the Buccaneers
description:
Dan Patrick discusses Tom Brady and how his personal life has impacted his play on the field. The guys conclude that we may unfortunately be starting to see "Crappy" Tom Brady. Plus, is it still possible for the Bucs to still win the division, and are the Lakers tanking?
